race.description: Ladbrokes Punter Assist Qtis Maiden Plate
race.comment: Lots of these are close to a win and a few handy-looking first starters as well. LADY WILLPOWER (10) will be tough to beat though. Four start maiden who really hasn't run a bad race including two minors. Just missed latest and can go one better. VOUCHERS (7) is a former Hayes galloper making debut in this area. Showed some ability in Victoria and expected to measure up in this line-up. NEXT STOP JUPITER (12) is a three-year-old filly on debut from the stable of Clinton Taylor. By Admire Mars from Unforgivable. From a good family and has the blinkers on. Pay to watch for any positive betting moves. HIGH SOBRIETY (15) is better this last run and with the claim and a decent draw will give a sight at odds.
